# gpg and YubiKey
Install the following before running `setup`:

    $ apt-get install gnupg-agent scdaemon pcscd pcsc-tools

Ensure that `gpg2` is always used:

    $ ln -s /usr/bin/gpg2 /usr/local/bin/gpg

Yubico ppa:

    $ sudo apt-add-repository ppa:yubico/stable
    $ sudo apt-get update
    $ sudo apt-get install yubikey-personalization-gui yubikey-neo-manager yubikey-personalization

